{"tid":1548891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世][最終文宣] 喚醒對中共既不信任 聯合世界圍堵#Chinazi","createTime":"2019-09-07T06:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:47:41.000Z","uid":117906,"like":87,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fa2dae1e3e62d2e34793fa32404caa394fa7e6","tid":1548891,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:52:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>搞清楚 最終目標一定係抗共 <br />\n認清事實 對準政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1. 五大訴求 遙遙無期</strong></span><br />\n拖左接近三個月 先回應一個<br />\n然後再不斷放風話 無可能做獨立調查<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 五大訴求 之後呢？</span></strong><br />\n就算大團圓結局 五大訴求回應晒 <br />\n（先不論就算真雙普選 特首都要中共任命）<br />\n一路而黎中共對香港既滲透  同 港共既腐敗媚共<br />\n大家無可能當無事發生過！<br />\n<br />\n-23條<br />\n-國教<br />\n-消滅廣東話<br />\n-大白象<br />\n-監控橙柱<br />\n-種票 <br />\n（種票想講多少少：民建聯就不嬲蛇齋餅糉加掌心雷，但至少佢地真係有針對老人家做好多地區工作，亦有多年地區工作經驗，呢一part係販民拍馬都追唔上。但近年既垃圾建制，睇下聯合鄉黑既何妖、假學歷既葛珮帆、幫新義安求情既鼠王芬，完全空降加種票入立法會，中共就係連民建聯都覺得唔夠紅！）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">呢堆問題既癥結就係中共<br />\n中共一日唔收皮<br />\n香港永遠都冇安落日子過！<br />\n所以聯合世界反#Chinazi係大方向！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對抗Chinazi可以聯合世界<br />\n同世界講 有個比Nazi更可惡既Chinazi ！<br />\n踐踏基本人權！<br />\n扭曲真相輸出假新聞！<br />\n殘殺自己國家人民！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（港獨可以係預想結果，但不能成為口號。因為歐美既選民會對民主、自由、反納粹有感覺；但唔會對一個咁遠但要爭取獨立既地方有感覺。只要佢地選民支持，政客就會做野，例如而家人權法案得美國兩黨支持）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cdebe24d960f5a94bb5f92668d11775af6237cf","tid":1548891,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63dbdd59bd68dbab9af293e72ecd47e136b32c8e","tid":1548891,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d728abd4da0690467d1c3506f366a37f9cfee7a","tid":1548891,"uid":140117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"105f7b3776a018054aeda44069870799313c1d19","tid":1548891,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"請幫手推"},{"pid":"95d123cb795e94ac72dc7cb4ac3b59921a3cb571","tid":1548891,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfd1e65aa06a2b9626c33db560456fb5d44d2db4","tid":1548891,"uid":225798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXp9xs3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXp9xs3.png&h=234b2311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UxWcs4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UxWcs4.png&h=8be5bf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTyFD74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTyFD74.png&h=b2f63fea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbb8827dc67e0da8c9325ee60af9d5938a9be632","tid":1548891,"uid":64012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bb9c53c7053353db1a9f01747bd5ca01b3a480e","tid":1548891,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit